name: Let There be Light by Alpine x Obvious

metadata.description: ’Let There Be Light’ is Alpine’s Genesis Collection built on three tiers of NFTs: Legendary, Ultra Rare and Common. Inspired by the A110 Sastruga Art Car, Alpine takes their collaboration with French Art Collective Obvious to the next level with an NFT Collection of AI-Generated artworks.
